      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FORTUNE STAR (4) won well two back before a 1.5L defeat over this track and trip when the race favourite. He stuck on well from midfield there but drawing inside may have hindered his chances. He's likely to be back in the run again here, but that may suit him better and this looks a nice scenario to return to winning ways. AMAZING AWARD (5) missed by 0.8L at this track and trip last start in that same race that FORTUNE STAR comes through. He sat on the speed there and was very strong to the line. This looks to shape similarly from the draw and he can go one better this time around. HARMONY GALAXY (3) gets Bowman in the saddle today from an inside draw despite some disappointing performances recently. He'll be able to sit handier from the inside this time and he can put his best foot forward. TO INFINITY (7) comes through the Stormi race were he was strong as a 30-1 chance. Can go close again.",
